      <div xml:id="Aink5-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink5">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
<l>          paciyil lākuka piṇicē ṇīṅkuka</l>
<l>          veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
<l>          mutalaip pōttu muḻumī ṉārun</l>
<l>          taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ ṟērem</l>
<l>          muṉkaṭai niṟka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          “May Ātaṉ prosper, may Aviṉi prosper.</l>
<l>          May there be no hunger, may sickness leave into the distance”,</l>
<l>          thus wants our mother. We,</l>
<l>          “the chariot of the man from the village by the cool ghat,</l>
<l>          where the male of the crocodile becomes full of whole fish,</l>
<l>          let it stand at our front gate”, thus we want.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
